  <brief_title>Reduction of Infection in Neonatal Intensive Care Units Using the Evidence-based Practice for Improving Quality</brief_title>
  <official_title>Reduction of Infection in Neonatal Intensive Care Units Using the Evidence-based Practice for Improving Quality: A Cluster Randomised Trial</official_title>
