  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Infants born at &lt;34 weeks' gestation

          -  Admitted to the participating NICUs within 7 days after birth

          -  Admitted to the participating NICUs between May 1, 2015 and April 30, 2018

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Infants with major congenital anomalies

          -  Infants who are moribund on admission (a decision is made to provide only palliative
             care)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
